title: Silver II Jungle LF ranked team
body:
Hello summoners, I am a silver II jungle main trying to find a ranked team that will be on quite frequently and not on randomly. I am looking for a team that is either serious or semi serious, just as long as we aim to rank up the ranked team ladder then I'm fine with it. My jungle champion pool at the moment is:

. Kindred
. Rek'sai
. Nunu
. Gragas
. Lee Sin
. Maokai
. Nidalee
. Jarvan IV

Last but not least for communication I can use skype, curse voice and teamspeak depending on the team.

If you want me to join your team then please add me on my account "LoveTigerLove" and I will try and respond as soo as possible.
